EN:
LALALALICENCE (LLLL) ver.1.0 (Unofficial as hell)

You can use my public projects pretty much however you like.
Personal use? Go wild. Students? Even better—learn something and make it cooler.

If you’re a company or making money with it, I’d appreciate a quick chat first.
Not because I’m greedy, just... you know, manners.

Use everything at your own risk.
This stuff comes “as is,” powered by caffeine and sleep deprivation.
If it breaks your PC or your sanity, I take no responsibility whatsoever.
I try not to ship disasters, but no promises. :D

